(43, 11, 45, 43, 10, 41, 41, 'believed on him', 'Belief in Jesus'' Truth', 'Both passages emphasize the belief in Jesus based on the testimonies of others. In John 11:45, many believed after witnessing Jesus'' miracles, while in John 10:41, people acknowledged the truth of John''s words about Jesus.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
