(43, 11, 46, 44, 5, 25, 25, 'went their ways to the Pharisees', 'Reporting Actions of Jesus and Apostles', 'This connection highlights the theme of individuals reporting significant actions to authorities. In both passages, people inform the Pharisees and the authorities about the activities of Jesus and the apostles, respectively.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
